  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of Integrated Multi-sectoral Assistance to Vulnerable Displaced Population in Somalia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In order to address the acute needs of displaced and vulnerable populations in Somalia, IOM provides a comprehensive and integrated health, water, sanitation and hygiene, camp coordination and camp management, displacement tracking matrix (DTM), and shelter and non-food item intervention, with the main objective to ensure dignified, safe and secure living conditions and basic services for vulnerable populations affected disasters driven by natural hazards and conflict.</narrative>
  </description>
